dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e83a98e5d287b6be44877b7c5de391e18332a650","tid":1569987,"uid":21432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:56:41.000Z","msg":"真係唔駛咁開心，土改成功的話，港資消失變晒中資，到時係度哈哈哈抵死既你都要打中資工，然後過時過節因為生計問題被逼拎住支那國旗係度鳩叫I am China Man。<br />\n<br />\n當然，如果你話I have no stake in the society，然後期望全部人攬炒既話你算係成功左一大半，恭喜你。<br />\n<br />\n各位仍然抗爭既巴打，請記得：<br />\n盡能力減少你地每一分能夠被支那賺到既錢"},{"pid":"afcdedaf7ebb2a1c6c068f316dc047d4ab477e11","tid":1569987,"uid":25424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"將會超低價回收土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同當年支共玩公私合營一樣，超低價逼你俾共產黨入股，過一兩年正式收歸國有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65061b7a5d82159d3e0c87ec7b1d0f8c938e127","tid":1569987,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:06:25.000Z","msg":"新界佬幫打,最後打埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4c130a4723050aba60d10d0f77c52bb2b01cf4","tid":1569987,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:09:23.000Z","msg":"all in內房股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daab7c806b33af86af717882bbc0dc431d0a84e4","tid":1569987,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T01:16:32.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b786018c3866975c410cd54f8c5574147c001e79","tid":1569987,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bed040945afe3797a3459afae65f627f0cf579a","tid":1569987,"uid":161863,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:05:10.000Z","msg":"新界佬一旱賣左地簽曬約俾地產商<br />\n今次最多係地產商入肉<br />\n班仆街牛屎佬唔受影響"},{"pid":"c4aff5dd18f0f713aaf998172c7ac7bc880e88ff","tid":1569987,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得：人多就打，人少就跑</span>"},{"pid":"3497646ccbd2681e2e22bd63f3e4de12c84b1a2e","tid":1569987,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:37:43.000Z","msg":"過去三十年,政府無認真處理土地問題, 地產商又貪得無厭 (例如:<br />\n<br />\n昨日有地產商居然同記者講樓宇空置稅對豪宅發展商不公平;<br />\n發大建築面積;<br />\n亂計實用率; <br />\n起發水樓;<br />\n起偽豪宅;<br />\n住客會所大一大, 單位面積細一細;<br />\n擠牙膏賣樓; <br />\n買家資信不透明; <br />\n以功能組別支持政府為由, 向政府伸手拿經濟著數; 等等)。<br />\n<br />\n根本如果政府狠狠解決土地問題的話, 年青示威者會少大半。君不見示威者大部分住新界?<br />\n<br />\n好啦,依家中國要對付地產商啦, 一個二個(新鴻基, 嘉華, 恒基, 信和,長實(走得快), 新世界, 會德豐) 俾人抄家問你驚未<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793904615fa4c417d6168e4a438fa6d4c8831bc9","tid":1569987,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"so? 佢指出一個必然悲觀既結論, 然後呢?<br />\n所有人幫襯琥珀教育去英國升學?"},{"pid":"ac0af33e2630fbd7510bebc8108bc410e6b45255","tid":1569987,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"793904615fa4c417d6168e4a438fa6d4c8831bc9","tid":1569987,"uid":306180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"so? 佢指出一個必然悲觀既結論, 然後呢?<br />\n所有人幫襯琥珀教育去英國升學?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"哈哈"}]}